{"generated":"2026-03-21T15:33:32.362252+00:00","period_start":"2026-03-15T12:57:00+00:00","period_end":"2026-03-21T15:30:00+00:00","snapshot_count":90,"html":"<h1>THE VENDETTA GAZETTE</h1>\n<h2>SPECIAL BLOOD & BULLETS EDITION — March 21, 2026</h2>\n\n<h3>GANG WAR ERUPTS AS \"IRON FIST\" WU-TANG AND \"THE CAPRICE KID\" TERRORIZE UNDERWORLD</h3>\n\n<p><strong>VENDETTA CITY</strong> — The streets ran red with blood this week as two merciless kingpins carved up the territory map like a Thanksgiving turkey! In a spectacular display of underworld brutality, the notorious <strong>Wu-Tang, \"The Iron Fist of the East Side,\"</strong> and the dapper yet deadly <strong>Sir Caprice, \"The Caprice Kid,\"</strong> unleashed twin reigns of terror that left the criminal establishment quaking in their spats!</p>\n\n<p>The Caprice Kid seized a breathtaking <em>99 turfs</em> in his lightning campaign, while the Iron Fist Wu-Tang wasn't far behind with <em>92 freshly conquered territories</em>. Together, these two titans of terror claimed nearly half of all new criminal real estate, sending lesser hoods scurrying for cover like rats from a sinking speakeasy!</p>\n\n<p>\"<em>Vacation Steve</em>\" — apparently back from his holiday with a renewed appetite for violence — muscled his way to third place with 53 new holdings, proving that rest and relaxation only sharpened his killer instincts. Not to be outdone, his apparent associate <strong>\"Vacation Albert\"</strong> grabbed 39 turfs of his own, suggesting this murderous duo's recent getaway was more strategy session than pleasure cruise!</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<strong>SPECIAL BULLETIN!</strong><br>\n<em>HQ MASSACRE ON MARCH 20th!</em><br><br>\nIn scenes reminiscent of the infamous Valentine's Day slaughter, Wu-Tang \"The Iron Fist\" stormed no fewer than <strong>THREE HEADQUARTERS</strong> in a single blood-soaked day! The bodies of Aharhibaba, 2345p, and Muna's entire crews were found riddled with Thompson slugs. Meanwhile, Sir Caprice wasn't idle — his boys knocked over Joshie's stronghold the same evening! Police report finding nothing but empty safes and chalk outlines!\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>But while some rise, others fall hard in this unforgiving game! The once-mighty <strong>StreetKing</strong> saw his empire crumble, losing 26 valuable territories as rival gangs picked his organization clean. The grandiose <em>\"FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR\"</em> — whose royal pretensions proved no match for street justice — hemorrhaged 20 turfs, while the ice-cold <strong>Ustaz Ice</strong> melted under pressure, surrendering an identical 20 territories to hungrier wolves.</p>\n\n<h3>FRESH BLOOD AND VANISHING ACTS PLAGUE THE UNDERWORLD</h3>\n\n<p>Six new desperadoes muscled their way onto Vendetta City's criminal scene this week, including the military-minded <strong>\"John James Rambo\"</strong> — complete with his trademark blood insignia — and the space-age racketeer <em>\"Flash Gordon.\"</em> Each carved out their initial territory with ruthless efficiency, proving that in this town, ambition and a smoking gun are all a man needs!</p>\n\n<p>However, Dame Fortune's wheel spins both ways, and a staggering <strong>49 criminal enterprises</strong> vanished into thin air! Whether they met their maker courtesy of rival tommy guns or simply fled to friendlier climates, these vanished villains leave behind only empty warehouses and unpaid debts. Among the disappeared: the mysteriously monikered <em>\"c,\"</em> the predatory <strong>\"wolf street,\"</strong> and the martial arts master <em>\"KungFuPanda\"</em> — proving that even ancient fighting techniques are no match for modern gangland justice!</p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\"